title: Billy Ray Cyrus Tells the Untold Story of Old Town Road + Bobby takes New Suggestions for Go-To Karaoke Song + Bobby Addresses Some Off-Air Drama in the Post Show Pre-Show
itunes:title: Billy Ray Cyrus Tells the Untold Story of Old Town Road + Bobby takes New Suggestions for Go-To Karaoke Song + Bobby Addresses Some Off-Air Drama in the Post Show Pre-Show
description:
Bobby addresses some off-air drama on the Post Show Pre-Show.  Billy Ray Cyrus stops by as the Friday Morning Conversation and tells us how he got added to Old Town Road. Bobby goes through new suggestions for a go-to karaoke song.
